default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSet the pay of 
defaultChief Executives and other senior executives.
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSpecify and review conditions under which the Chief Executive and Human Resources manager have delegated control of the pay of other staff, including pensions, and how they will report to the Board.
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEnsure that
default pay 
defaultlevels correspond with any other policies the charity may have, such as a risk policy.
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDetermine appropriate targets if the charity uses performance-related pay.
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultRemain aware of major changes in employee benefits, including pay, pensions and other rew
defaultards.
